>Description:
The settings are described in the tools manual by a
paragraph that begins with

  The settings in this structure reflect the settings ...

The various settings that are mentioned should be indexed.
Withtout that, it is almost impossible to figure out what
the settings do -- for example, try to find in the manual
what `insert-lines' does.
